Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1446,571.5)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}謝謝你告訴我這麼多小巖井先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1321.5,618)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}說起過去的我實在很慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1746,664.5)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}不過終於釋懷了
